description.Name: description
description.Value: The Mens Qualifications run by Joel Hedrick on Day 3 of the US Freestyle Mogul Skiing Selections event. The event hosted United States mogul skiing athletes from the US Freestyle team as well as clubs across the United States. There were also international mogul skiing athletes from Japan, Poland, Great Britain, Iran and Australia, including athletes from the New South Wales Institute of Sport (NSWIS) and the Mogul Skiing Academy. Check out www.mogulskiingacademy.com/videos for more videos from the event.
